" listchar=trail is not as flexible, use the below to highlight trailing whitespace
func! ShowTrailingWS()
    highlight ExtraWhitespace ctermbg=yellow guibg=yellow
    match ExtraWhitespace /\s\+$/
endfunc
nnoremap <F6> :call ShowTrailingWS()<CR>

